# Step 5 – What Will the App Need?

Let's list the major components.

### Mobile App (Flutter)

What the user sees.

---

### Backend (FastAPI)

Handles requests and business logic.

---

### Database (PostgreSQL)

Stores users and blood tests.

---

### OCR Service

Reads values from uploaded reports.

---

### AI Service

Explains the reports.

---

### Cloud Storage

Stores PDFs and images.

